Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:14.84,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}但也没有动摇到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.84,0:24:17.68,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}仅此唯一属于我们两人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.20,0:24:21.12,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}即便明天会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:24.92,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}但你却依然不变
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:26.72,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.72,0:24:28.36,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}你是那么地不可取代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.36,0:24:31.32,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}因为一直陪伴在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.48,0:24:34.76,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}你相信无可匹敌的爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.88,0:24:38.28,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}现在所感受到的这无可匹敌的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.64,0:24:39.48,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}我会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.96,0:24:43.00,ED CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\3a&H55\fad(100,100)}今晚就让你看到
